text:
Great streaming ever, and also the longest "Ohayou" and "Konbanwa"

Also the laughter, the great highlight.

The boxing match... the jokes about it: "In the Right Corner, with 144 cm. and aprox. 43 kg., the champion Uruha "Desksmasher" Rushia", and also "Fly as Butterfly in the huge Night Sky and Stings like a Wasp"
(About Butterfly is also a reference for her original song "Butterflies in the huge night sky", I hope she is practicing it)

And also the Agonic Victory in Baseball... presumably Rushia would be the new "Princess 9" (In allusion to the 1998 Anime series)

Supaachaato Orei Taimu is now called Supaacha Yomi Taimu, since previous stream.
